  m_text: "Wow, it looks like the heroes managed to reach the last room! But don\u2019t
    worry, you still have an ace up your sleeve: the boss! When heroes reach the
    last room, SMOL will be able to use his power to possess a powerful creature
    to fend off the last of the heroes."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d64da69360c2c66489c9deeb5f1c79c7, type: 2}
