  m_text: When the boss phase starts, SMOL will automatically possess the boss selected
    at the beginning of the run and can control it during the fight. You will be
    able to use different actions to fight and defeat the heroes to win the day and
    survive even longer. Every boss has different actions, so choose your favorite!
